ul74rk" loading="lazy"/></picture></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="54a08c90-98b5-412d-b619-de60a33c1dfb" class="r-1vldepm"><div data-rid="9b3e87ac-d648-4b2d-8c62-8fc0347aa2dc" class="r-64nl5e"><div data-rid="e9e684db-fb20-467f-9ee7-ee720af1f68a" class="r-17mhcri"><div data-rid="dfecff17-9208-4d73-9987-70ec7d7d03e1" class="r-syftsh alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>FAQs</p></span></div><div data-rid="0fe323e0-67f3-4af0-b248-8f1f7c8419c6" class="r-1jak70r" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="60325c58-3475-48ad-a711-ff36053b351f" class="r-tra09i" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="73d2824f-8627-4477-ae0d-7ffe3c806ad3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R6f32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-7tfpi5"><div data-rid="b8d99244-8771-44da-bb5c-e740497b13cf" class="r-spxp3w alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Why can't I just pay once?</p></span></div><div data-rid="52cdb211-beb9-4c7e-9cf8-144a1e71b3e1" class="r-auo480" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1k1h7t6" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R6f32:"><div data-rid="b9256c4e-e5a5-4f95-8ade-266172af045a" class="r-1msqecl"><div data-rid="96b52724-d9c4-4f10-8619-21691e19562d" class="r-1tx1yqo alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Your membership powers the platform that connects your devices, processes your data, and delivers AI and software updates. A one-time purchase would mean a frozen product. Arccos is built to keep getting better.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="6267df1b-3307-4177-94ce-0de6410a13da" class="r-13dmhek" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="7d0104b5-5bbf-4c41-bb4a-50f2136c6dcf" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Raf32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-65wkka"><div data-rid="352f2e2d-2592-435e-bd58-3715d399a2a1" class="r-cagf7h alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Can I pause during the offseason? </p></span></div><div data-rid="f77f931b-bddd-4962-9da5-6a1d8dc2b5d2" class="r-vs8b7v" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-bspbwt" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Raf32:"><div data-rid="be0c771a-7f81-4f69-a144-2759a94c83cb" class="r-l41acl"><div data-rid="7eb2a7dc-80e2-48a8-91b7-d829ae30e237" class="r-5mvo20 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>We don't currently offer a pause option. To keep your membership as simple and affordable as possible, we focus on annual subscriptions.  </p><p><br></p><p>For most golfers, the subscription is a small fraction of total golf expenditure, and a modest cost on a per-round basis. So the edge that Arccos gives you will quickly pay for itself. Many Arccos members also find they play more as they improve, and travel to play at any time of year.  </p><p><br></p><p>If you still have questions, or need to cancel, you can contact us at [<a href="mailto:starter@arccosgolf.com">starter@arccosgolf.com</a>]. Every round, stroke, and stat is saved. So you can reactivate when you're ready and pick up exactly where you left off.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="2b79700b-e584-46ed-b227-352feaa885f8" class="r-cpc5cf" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="845a8418-2c71-4e4c-b387-071ab115792f" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Ref32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-139tbnx"><div data-rid="4fe85157-a5ea-4bf1-855d-135b8a557b34" class="r-e1eyhi alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What's the difference between Arccos Air and Smart Sensors? </p></span></div><div data-rid="7a5e885b-b148-4052-9ac1-0695aa2fb8f6" class="r-jajlm4" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-nm1fx4" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Ref32:"><div data-rid="b380d4bb-991d-4ceb-8b5e-4f3fe9769812" class="r-1c7370q"><div data-rid="327d1157-170f-4c64-a6ba-6bc774dface8" class="r-1b9u57 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Similar features. Different setup. Air tracks shots without the need for a phone in your pocket, nor sensors on your clubs, for the quickest, easiest way to track every shot. Smart Sensors provide automatic club tagging, when paired with your phone or Apple Watch, or in combination with the Air wearable. Use both together, for the richest data and phone-free convenience.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="3c650c31-1d65-4ea4-9e91-fba0d7348d71" class="r-1ho64yt" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="000a61c6-c62d-4021-9adb-161ed4dedbf3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rif32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-q7pwd6"><div data-rid="cc07d647-1412-40f5-ba74-f75bb65c3a5d" class="r-1prl0jq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What happens to my data if I cancel?</p></span></div><div data-rid="6b066fc9-9664-4787-9589-4617b923bb38" class="r-dk5jxp" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1yn54yd" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rif32:"><div data-rid="21eaced0-915e-4697-8024-28bb9cf24843" class="r-vxxcy1"><div data-rid="fbd7d99b-c6dd-4169-8d31-4586908b40f6" class="r-7iq8gl alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>It stays in your account. Renew your membership anytime and it's all there.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="6c4cb8a7-41ff-4a65-8869-3966c3430dd6" class="r-jvkyl5" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="c902d767-0dba-4014-97f0-8b4757b9af5b" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rmf32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-18tbax1"><div data-rid="6c7c6735-ddb8-477b-851c-597ef1ec90fc" class="r-myfpe8 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Why does a range finder need a membership?</p></span></div><div data-rid="418ee86c-7c82-4806-9c0c-b4b07d43df20" class="r-e2731n" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-j0j6im" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rmf32:"><div data-rid="17dc8a45-50a1-4afe-8c76-9cfd221a6079" class="r-h4xgbu"><div data-rid="2894b78d-1e54-410c-87e0-81fb129ca59c" class="r-17rytfg alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>The Arccos Smart Laser Rangefinder requires a membership because it is a real-time device. It syncs with real-time data, including wind and weather for your precise location to calculate "plays like" distances. Plus membership gives you access to cutting edge shot-by-shot AI Strategy based on your specific data and tendencies, up-to-date Green Maps for 1000's of courses, and free software updates.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="f04dbced-3b0a-43b0-ab1b-31f8a900b240" class="r-j3667d" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="f85fff7d-e3bf-4181-8b51-6d2d4a50aea6" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rqf32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-nry3g7"><div data-rid="9c2fc3de-d3f7-4300-a18a-e276dfbf8ead" class="r-f7p0nf alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Do I need Game Tracking to use the Smart Laser? </p></span></div><div data-rid="78227385-453f-4496-b92f-d618a9c80ce1" class="r-1f7nsfc" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1v8t98c" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rqf32:"><div data-rid="392c16c7-1c58-40ca-9e42-1ede08d870fc" class="r-5bt28k"><div data-rid="05255338-fdd5-4df5-b2e7-12765be48db1" class="r-1qjiwoj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>No. Smart Laser works on its own. Add Game Tracking later if you want.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="c18c98f7-7463-40dd-a164-1bc3a5cba801" class="r-ltmffc" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="e2160f49-1f01-409f-ac7a-9ab5ad2d14f9" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Ruf32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1x1c8gp"><div data-rid="5d466c83-4b14-4ea5-b56d-0e65fda7b8e4" class="r-14d6agq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Is the data accurate? </p></span></div><div data-rid="6c17fbc3-7bb2-4c31-a2fd-ccd4cf9dea65" class="r-1ryakp6" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-12n21pp" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Ruf32:"><div data-rid="385401c8-22ae-493b-87c4-5483ec8686e4" class="r-1t5oqxf"><div data-rid="53dfa6ea-1533-4e4d-9ecd-907cef6f8cd8" class="r-17g5izj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>1.5 billion shots tracked. Validated by PGA TOUR players. 15+ patents. For the Smart Laser, "Plays Like" distances are accurate to 1 yard, from up to 999 yards, and based on 800,000 real-world measurements.</p></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><picture data-rid="11ba3b6e-5c88-41fe-b632-f6456c310a07" class="r-2dq3g7"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/824a366a-dafd-4375-8504-aacc62618158/22f65a36-8796-450b-b532-ce91e0a73d78?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/824a366a-dafd-4375-8504-aacc62618158/22f65a36-8796-450b-b532-ce91e0a73d78?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/824a366a-dafd-4375-8504-aacc62618158/22f65a36-8796-450b-b532-ce91e0a73d78?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/824a366a-dafd-4375-8504-aacc62618158/22f65a36-8796-450b-b532-ce91e0a73d78" class="r-1j7fnw1" loading="eager"/></picture></div></div></div></div><style>@import url(https://